import { Box, Button, TextField } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";

export default function Login() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <form noValidate autoComplete="off">
                <TextField 
                label="Email"
                name="email"
                variant="outlined"
                />
                <TextField 
                label="Name"
                name="name"
                variant="outlined"
                />
                <Button 
                type ="submit"
                variant="contained"
                size="large">Start</Button>
            </form>
        </Box>
    )
}
